h President Emmanuel Macron's plan to propose a ceasefire during this summer's Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 4024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3866, \"end\": 3872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999964502634859, \"rank\": 2.0663787906482324e-06, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 3925, \"end\": 3941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 3942, \"end\": 3957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron\\u00a0said in an interview from Paris shown on Ukrainian television on Saturday that\\u00a0Russia would be asked to observe a ceasefire, in line with the customary host country's appeal for peace.\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4026, \"end\": 4032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5773972763323985e-21, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 4059, \"end\": 4064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999966257747, \"rank\": 3.3744133168927908e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4074, \"end\": 4094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Ukraine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ukrainian television\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 4112, \"end\": 4118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999964502634859, \"rank\": 2.0663787906482324e-06, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vladimir Putin said Russia's interests would always take precedence, but he would consider the request:  \\\"We are for peaceful negotiations, but not because the enemy is running out of ammunition.\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4219, \"end\": 4233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.132588363646676e-23, \"text\": \"Vladimir Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 4239, \"end\": 4245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999964502634859, \"rank\": 2.0663787906482324e-06, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are for it, if they really seriously want to build peaceful, good neighbourly relations between the two states in the long term, instead of taking a pause for one and a half or for two years to rearm,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The call for a ceasefire comes after Macron recently said that sending Western troops into Ukraine should not be ruled out - though he said the current situation does not require it and insisted Russia cannot be allowed to win the war.\", \"from\": 4630, \"to\": 4865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4667, \"end\": 4673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5773972763323985e-21, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 4721, \"end\": 4728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999875157833987, \"rank\": 1.2469654686775236e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 4825, \"end\": 4831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999964502634859, \"rank\": 2.0663787906482324e-06, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee in December decided against a blanket ban of Russian and Belarusian athletes over the invasion of Ukraine.\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 5009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4871, \"end\": 4902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4948, \"end\": 4955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9645580444315556, \"rank\": 0.033838111972786286, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc